────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
This project builds on the M5StickC Plus inverted-pendulum kit and example
firmware originally created and shared by ニンシン (n_shinichi):

    https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:6440184
    https://github.com/nsinichi/M5_inverted

Many thanks to the original author for releasing the design and code that
made this learning project possible.  See README.md → "謝辞 / Acknowledgments"
for details.
